 1999-07361999-04-220,  HERITAGE,  LAB,  ,  , 
PrecisEnactment of the STATUS OF THE ARTIST ACT PROFESSIONAL CATEGORY REGULATIONS which allow self-employed professionals (such as camera operators, costume designers, hairstylists, make-up artists, etc.) who contribute to the creation of a production, to take advantage of the legal framework for collective bargaining set out in the Act.
